  "title": "Issue with ais-dynamic-widgets and ais-hierarchical-menu in Vue3",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\r\n\r\nWe are trying to use `ais-dynamic-widgets` in combination with `ais-hierarchical-menu` using the following versions:\r\n\r\n- `algoliasearch`: `4.12.1`  \r\n- `vue`: `3.2.25`  \r\n- `vue-instantsearch`: `4.19.4`  \r\n\r\nThe `ais-hierarchical-menu` works perfectly on its own. However, when placed inside the `ais-dynamic-widgets`, nothing is rendered within the dynamic widget.  \r\n\r\nIs this an expected behavior, or are we missing something in our configuration?  \r\n\r\n![2024-12-20 13_26_36-instantsearch-app – Mozilla Firefox](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3c7bedc9-d90a-4f93-8a07-bbaa4024bf9b)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nThe following code is in our `App.vue` \r\nEven with `facet=\"['*']\"` gone it doesn't work.\r\n\r\n```\r\n<template>\r\n  <div class=\"container\">\r\n    <ais-instant-search\r\n      :search-client=\"searchClient\"\r\n      index-name=\"test\"\r\n      >\r\n      <ais-dynamic-widgets :facet=\"['*']\">\r\n          <ais-hierarchical-menu :attributes=\"categories\" />\r\n      </ais-dynamic-widgets>\r\n    </ais-instant-search>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script>\r\nimport algoliasearch from 'algoliasearch/lite';\r\nimport { AisDynamicWidgets, AisHierarchicalMenu  } from 'vue-instantsearch/vue3/es';\r\n\r\nexport default {\r\n  components: {\r\n    AisDynamicWidgets,\r\n    AisHierarchicalMenu\r\n  },\r\n  data() {\r\n    return {\r\n      searchClient: algoliasearch(\r\n        'secret',\r\n        'secret'\r\n      ),\r\n      categories: ['categoryLevel0', 'categoryLevel1', 'categoryLevel2', 'categoryLevel3']\r\n    };\r\n  },\r\n};\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Live reproduction\r\n\r\nsandbox Vue doens't work?\r\n\r\n### 💭 Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThe `ais-hierarchical-menu` should render properly inside the `ais-dynamic-widgets`, with minimal code. \r\n\r\n### Package version\r\n\r\nalgoliasearch 4.12.1,  vue 3.2.25, vue-instantsearch 4.19.4  \r\n\r\n### Operating system\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Browser\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Code of Conduct\r\n\r\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
